OCESQL     CALL "OCESQLDisconnect" USING
OCESQL          BY REFERENCE SQLCA
OCESQL     END-CALL
               IF SQLCODE NOT EQUAL ZERO
                   DISPLAY 'ERREUR DISCONNECT: SQLCODE=' SQLCODE
               END-IF
               MOVE 'N' TO WS-CONNECTED-FLAG
           END-IF.